item.description: Strength is the basis for all movement, injury prevention, recovery and rehabilitation. hysical strength is the most important thing in life. This is true whether you want it to be or not. Mark Rippetoe In life I try not to live at the extremes. I always set a goals and have a focus, but I try to keep perspective.
